lyrics:
[verse]
Anurag, the poet with a melancholic soul
Lost in thoughts, his emotions take control
Longing for love, his heart feels heavy
Seeking solace in verses, he finds sanctuary

[chorus]
Oh Anurag, let your words paint the night
Express your pain, make the darkness ignite
Your muse awaits, her touch to heal
In your verses, let your desires reveal
